The paper focuses on IoT security and privacy, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of machine learning technologies for clustering and semantic analysis suggests that the paper may also fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) and social and information networks (cs.SI). The discussion of liability and open research problems suggests that the paper may also fall under cyber law and cybercrime (cs.CY) and software engineering (cs.SE).
